title: CoolMedia Cool Burning Studio v5.0.1+Serial-TeamGBZ
description: With Cool Burning Studio you can make high-quality audio recordings from any external source. Cool Burning Studio can record any sound passing through any line of your sound card. For example, you can record sound being played back by an external program(including the playback of Internet broadcasts and Internet-telephony conversations), sound from a microphone and much more.
